436
00:23:49,186 --> 00:23:50,906
To je tablet.

437
00:23:50,906 --> 00:23:52,537
Tentoraz sa buchli po vrecku.

438
00:23:52,537 --> 00:23:54,302
Áno, konečne.

439
00:23:54,302 --> 00:23:56,617
Niekedy vedia robiť aj pekné veci.

440
00:23:56,617 --> 00:24:00,340
